<hgroup><h1>Accuracy of an Automated Knowledge Base for Identifying Drug Adverse Reactions</h1></hgroup><div class="cg p">
<a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Voss%20EA"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id1"><span class="name western">EA Voss</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id1">
