<div class="p">
<sup>d</sup>University of Pittsburgh, Pittsburgh, PA</div>
<div class="p">
<sup>c</sup>Observational Health Data Sciences and Informatics (OHDSI), New York, NY</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Boyce%20RD"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">RD Boyce</span></a>
</div>
