<div class="tw-foot p">
<div class="fn" id="TFN5"><p id="P92">OMOP: Observational Medical Outcomes Partnership, EU-ADR: Exploring and Understanding Adverse Drug Reactions, AUC: area under the curve, LBCI: lower bound 95% confidence interval, UPCI: upper bound 95% confidence interval, FAERS: FDA Adverse Event Reporting System, PRR: proportional reporting ratio</p></div>
